---
const stats = [
  { value: "7+ años", label: "Datos a producción" },
  { value: "AWS", label: "Cloud & Data Engineering" },
  { value: "Data + AI", label: "BI, ML & Analytics" },
];
---

<section id="top" class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">Data Engineering &amp; Analytics Leader</span>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Convierto datos en
        <span class="grad">decisiones que mueven el negocio</span>.
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Soy <strong>Matías Roubaud</strong>, ingeniero con +7 años llevando datos
        a producción de punta a punta: desde pipelines escalables en AWS hasta
        dashboards ejecutivos y modelos de ML. Hoy lidero una función de Datos &amp;
        AI, y ayudo a empresas a construir la infraestructura que necesitan para
        decidir con datos confiables.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary">Trabajemos juntos →</a>
        <a href="#servicios" class="btn btn-ghost">Ver servicios</a>
      </div>

      <ul class="hero-stats">
        {stats.map((s) => (
          <li>
            <span class="stat-value">{s.value}</span>
            <span class="stat-label">{s.label}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="code-card">
        <div class="code-bar">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span>
          <em>pipeline.py</em>
        </div>
        <pre><code><span class="c-key">from</span> pipeline <span class="c-key">import</span> extract, load

<span class="c-fn">@orchestrate</span>(schedule=<span class="c-str">"@daily"</span>)
<span class="c-key">def</span> <span class="c-fn">run</span>():
    raw = extract.from_source(<span class="c-str">"crm"</span>)
    clean = transform(raw).dedupe()
    load.to_warehouse(clean, <span class="c-str">"analytics"</span>)
    <span class="c-key">return</span> <span class="c-num">"✓ 1.2M rows"</span></code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
  }

  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5.2vw, 3.6rem);
    margin: 4px 0 20px;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .grad {
    background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.12rem;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .hero-sub strong { color: var(--text); }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 36px;
    list-style: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 26px;
  }

  .stat-value {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  /* Code card visual */
  .code-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    overflow: hidden;
    transform: perspective(1200px) rotateY(-7deg) rotateX(3deg);
  }

  .code-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    background: var(--bg-soft);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .code-bar span {
    width: 11px;
    height: 11px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #2c3650;
  }

  .code-bar span:nth-child(1) { background: #ff5f57; }
  .code-bar span:nth-child(2) { background: #febc2e; }
  .code-bar span:nth-child(3) { background: #28c840; }

  .code-bar em {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  pre {
    padding: 22px 20px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .c-key { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .c-fn { color: var(--accent); }
  .c-str { color: #f0a868; }
  .c-num { color: #b48ef0; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .hero-visual { order: -1; }
    .code-card { transform: none; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-stats { gap: 20px; }
  }
</style>
